title: IN PICTURES: Sri Lankans in Melbourne engage in protests
body_lines: COLOMBO (News 1st); Sri Lankans in Melbourne, Australia engaged in a protest demanding for the President’s resignation at Melbourne Federation Square on Easter Sunday, today (17).
Norochcholai at risk of being inactive for 1 1/2 months if two coal ships are not unloaded
No move to utilize military against peaceful protests: Defence Ministry
